SSL test files for SMERP

Generate a CA certificate:
openssl req -nodes -days 1825 -x509 -newkey rsa:2048 -out smerpCA.cert.pem -keyout smerpCA.key.pem -outform PEM

Generate a certificate:
openssl req -new -nodes -keyout smerpd.key -out smerpd.req -days 365

Sign a certificate
openssl ca -cert smerpCA.cert.pem -policy policy_anything -out smerpd.crt -infiles smerpd.req
